wikimedia-privacypage: {{notranslate}} Default Wikimedia projects link to privacy policy. Should not be changed at the request of Wikimedia Foundation's Legal Department. Should not include 'Special:MyLanguage/'. Approved languages for links: en (primary for document), ar, de, es, fr, it, ja, pt-br
wikimedia-privacypage-labs: {{notranslate}} Default Wikimedia Labs projects link to terms of use. Should not be changed at the request of Wikimedia Foundation's Legal Department.
wikimedia-cookiestatement-page: {{notranslate}} Default link to Wikimedia Foundation cookie statement for the footer on all WMF sites.
